# ✈️ AI Travel Planner

AI-powered travel itinerary generator using Groq's Llama 3.3 model via LangChain.

## Features

- 🤖 AI-generated personalized itineraries
- 🎯 Interest-based recommendations
- 📊 Production-ready with ELK stack logging
- ☸️ Kubernetes deployment ready
- 🔒 Security hardened
- 📈 Auto-scaling support

